text: KLTO (99.1 FM) is a radio station broadcasting a Spanish language Top 40 (CHR) format to the Waco-Temple, Texas area. The station is owned by Waco Entertainment Group, LLC The transmitter is near Flat, Texas in Coryell County. ==References== ==External links== * LTO (FM) Category:Contemporary hit radio stations in the United States
